description=Auto-sorts downloads into categorized folders. NEW in v4.3.2: Native WebUI with on/off toggle, log viewer, volume key setup. v4.3.1: Magisk module detection. v4.3: Recursive scanning, auto-exclusion, custom exclusions. Works with Magisk and KernelSU.
